{"tid":2285733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[千人計劃]小心中大董咚博士指導的基因研究","createTime":"2020-11-14T10:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T14:58:50.000Z","uid":26770,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"126d02200e79c2b62b859e3f914bc2114ebfa91f","tid":2285733,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"[千人計劃]小心中大董咚博士指導的基因研究<br />\n原貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2285713/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2285713/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港成年人 基因素養 程度嘅大型研究<br />\n基因素養指的是對基因或遺傳學原理有足夠的知識和理解，牽涉對基因原理的態度，能為個人健康或安康做出明智的決定，並有效地參與有關基因或遺傳問題的社會決策。<br />\n<br />\nProf. Dong DONG畢業於U of Minnesota<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sphpc.cuhk.edu.hk/dongdong?lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sphpc.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fdongdong%3Flang%3Dzh&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=746314c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sphpc.cuhk.edu.hk/dongdong?lang=zh</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cfa.shufe-cec.com/p/32.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfa.shufe-cec.com%2Fp%2F32.html&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=10a5442f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cfa.shufe-cec.com/p/32.html</a><br />\n知名校友/師兄係田國強, 千人計劃首批專家, 位階好高<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\n1)香港警魔,深圳關口係無合理理由搶香港人基因資料,特別係異見人士<br />\n2)點解香港政府故意唔封關玩到疫情爆發再強推強制檢測?<br />\n3) 中國都大把人, 香港人基因特別?狗共千方百計攪香港基因庫原因?"},{"pid":"d91c82f4c8a4b64522653748f1070544be13c6e6","tid":2285733,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"玩到送IPHONE<br />\n<br />\n下一步香港政府可能攪自願驗身<br />\n驗完買自願醫保計劃有折都似<br />\n<br />\n你願意交DNA真係咩柒都送比你<br />\n你屋企有一條友貪小便宜交基因都奶野"},{"pid":"85356b9320a556928607014e60deabbbb1c94756","tid":2285733,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"值得你連開兩個post一定好緊要"},{"pid":"e7a2055dfcb89