55bd1ac3b5123488785928f5f56b68","tid":2285733,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wiki.mbalib.com/zh-tw/%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%BD%E5%BC%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.mbalib.com%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%25BC%25BA&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=e5c1a550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.mbalib.com/zh-tw/%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%BD%E5%BC%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n睇埋田國強係官方的底<br />\n<br />\n 田國強是教育部首批人文社會科學長江學者講座教授<br />\n<br />\n1992年─1994年6月任濟源市五龍口鎮鎮長、黨委副書記兼五龍口風景管理局局長，<br />\n<br />\n  1994年─1997年任濟源市招商局局長、黨組書記。<br />\n<br />\n  1997年4月─1998年5月任濟源市招商局局長、黨組書記兼外經委主任、黨委書記。<br />\n<br />\n  1998年5月&mdash;2006年12月任濟源市人民政府副市長。2006年12月至2007年2月任中共濟源市委常委、市委秘書長、市政府副市長。2007年2月至今任中共濟源市委常委、市委秘書長、市委辦公室主任。主持市委辦公室全面工作；協助薛興國同志處理市委日常工作。"},{"pid":"f479691885af9b25ed41c47b102a0b6942556f26","tid":2285733,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39426f3248d2ea3180b5ec8984beaa560a9f5703","tid":2285733,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74c37a9a7208f4b8ff4f1821947d6263a7364051","tid":2285733,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65e062b27b8071174cbac507c73462f94026fc66","tid":2285733,"uid":189234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"196c6162de2e3013d82e27254f8f215712e07be7","tid":2285733,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"呢個 Matt_Helders係由成TEAM5毛輪更<br />\n<br />\n24小時一見我出POST就瘋狂抹黑<br />\n係病態到用程式MON住搶第一頁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"又屈毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=